album.name: A Tribute to the Black Emperors

wiki.summary: A sample from the 1981 horror movie "The Evil Dead" is used in the beginning to "Wings of Funeral". A sample from a Swedish TV program is used for the opening of "My Dark Subconscious." Released also on a split bootleg with Mayhem entitled "Tribute to the Black Emperors" and bootleg split CD with Poison's ''Into the Abyss''. Morbid 1. My Dark Subconscious 2. Wings of Funera 3. From the Dark 4. Disgusting Demla Mayhem 5. The Freezing Moon 6. Necrolust 7. Funeral Fog 8. Carnage Read more on Last.fm.
